, "displayName": "Donald J. Trump", "username": "realDonaldTrump"}, "content": "The United States has spent EIGHT TRILLION DOLLARS fighting and policing in the Middle East. Thousands of our Great Soldiers have died or been badly wounded. Millions of people have died on the other side. GOING INTO THE MIDDLE EAST IS THE WORST DECISION EVER MADE.....", "parentTweet": false, "likes": 137714}}, "post_flair_text": "\u262a\ufe0f\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u262a\ufe0f", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "text", "uuid": "1ASZD1Ho7J", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 37, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8535505, "raw_content": "BHO appointed her to the DC District in '13.  JB elevated her to the DC circuit in 21.  She was only on the Appeals for 11 months.\n\nThis plan was put in place several years prior.  Constitutional knowledge and basic legal knowledge, along with a history of discretion and intelligent rulings, completely unnecessary and undesired.\n\nThey only need ideologues and will fill in the gaps to dupe the R's.  Then of course some of the R's are political trojan horses.\n\nProgressive judges only use the law for decoration.  They pick, choose, and extrapolate.  BTW, the Trump admin is compiling a darn good record on appeal.", "author": "dataonly", "created": 1775310081377, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "Mungo", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "Let's Be Very Clear->Ketanji Was Groomed for the Court by BHO and JB", "last_c